// ==========================================
// SECTION: PRINCIPIOS DE MARCA (TECH GRID)
// ==========================================
section(class="py-24 bg-background-dark border-y border-white/5 relative" id="brand-principles")
  //- Efecto de iluminación ambiental sutil
  div(class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-ritma-purple/5 blur-[120px] pointer-events-none")
  div(class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-96 h-96 bg-primary/5 blur-[120px] pointer-events-none")

  div(class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6")
    //- Encabezado de sección con estilo industrial
    div(class="mb-16 border-l-2 border-primary pl-6")
      h2(class="font-display font-black text-3xl text-white uppercase tracking-tighter") 
        | Core 
        span(class="text-primary") Pillars
      p(class="text-slate-500 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.4em] mt-2") Ritma System Architecture v1.0

    //- Grid con separación de 1px (estilo bento técnico)
    div(class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-px bg-white/5 border border-white/5")

      // ----------------------------
      // BLOQUE 01: MISIÓN
      // ----------------------------
      div(class="bg-background-dark p-12 relative group overflow-hidden transition-colors hover:bg-surface-dark/50" id="mission")
        //- Icono decorativo con rotación en hover
        div(class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-6 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-40 transition-all duration-500 group-hover:rotate-12")
          span(class="material-symbols-outlined text-7xl text-primary") dynamic_form

        div(class="relative z-10")
          div(class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6")
            span(class="size-2 bg-primary animate-pulse shadow-[0_0_8px_#C9DA2B]")
            span(class="text-[10px] font-bold text-primary tracking-[0.4em] uppercase") 01. MISIÓN
          
          h3(class="font-display font-extrabold text-2xl mb-6 uppercase text-white tracking-tighter leading-none")
            | Empoderar al 
            span(class="block text-primary") Ecosistema
          
          p(class="text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-10 font-body")
            | Proveer infraestructura digital robusta que permita a los DJs y productores latinos gestionar su carrera con autonomía técnica y financiera.
          
          //- Fader de progreso interactivo
          div(class="w-full h-[2px] bg-white/5 relative overflow-hidden")
            div(class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary w-1/3 group-hover:w-full transition-all duration-1000 ease-in-out")

      // ----------------------------
      // BLOQUE 02: VISIÓN
      // ----------------------------
      div(class="bg-background-dark p-12 relative group overflow-hidden transition-colors hover:bg-surface-dark/50" id="vision")
        div(class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-6 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-40 transition-all duration-500 group-hover:-translate-y-2")
          span(class="material-symbols-outlined text-7xl text-ritma-purple") rocket_launch

        div(class="relative z-10")
          div(class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6")
            span(class="size-2 bg-ritma-purple shadow-[0_0_8px_#A462A7]")
            span(class="text-[10px] font-bold text-ritma-purple tracking-[0.4em] uppercase") 02. VISIÓN
          
          h3(class="font-display font-extrabold text-2xl mb-6 uppercase text-white tracking-tighter leading-none")
            | Estándar 
            span(class="block text-ritma-purple") Regional
          
          p(class="text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-10 font-body")
            | Ser el núcleo tecnológico donde converge la creatividad musical y la innovación, elevando la calidad de la producción latina al estándar global.
          
          div(class="w-full h-[2px] bg-white/5 relative overflow-hidden")
            div(class="absolute inset-0 bg-ritma-purple w-2/3 group-hover:w-full transition-all duration-1000 ease-in-out")

      // ----------------------------
      // BLOQUE 03: VALORES
      // ----------------------------
      div(class="bg-background-dark p-12 relative group overflow-hidden transition-colors hover:bg-surface-dark/50" id="values")
        div(class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-6 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-40 transition-all duration-500 group-hover:scale-110")
          span(class="material-symbols-outlined text-7xl text-ritma-cyan") diversity_3

        div(class="relative z-10")
          div(class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6")
            span(class="size-2 bg-ritma-cyan shadow-[0_0_8px_#57C5D3]")
            span(class="text-[10px] font-bold text-ritma-cyan tracking-[0.4em] uppercase") 03. VALORES
          
          h3(class="font-display font-extrabold text-2xl mb-6 uppercase text-white tracking-tighter leading-none")
            | Comunidad 
            span(class="block text-ritma-cyan") & Ritmo
          
          p(class="text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-10 font-body")
            | Nuestra base es la transparencia, la innovación constante y el respeto profundo por la diversidad cultural de nuestras raíces.
          
          div(class="w-full h-[2px] bg-white/5 relative overflow-hidden")
            div(class="absolute inset-0 bg-ritma-cyan w-full transition-all")